      "type": "MRichText",
      "data": {
        "content": {
          "$i18n": {
            "zh-CN": "这里展示 docs_client_block 中由 @clientBlockDoc 注释同步而来的客户端 block 注册、工具箱、属性、默认值、保存规则、事件、方法和源码引用。页面编辑器的组件列表也会读取同一份后端 API 数据。",
            "en-US": "This page shows client block registration, toolbox settings, properties, defaults, save rules, events, methods, and source references synchronized from @clientBlockDoc annotations in docs_client_block. The page editor component list uses the same backend API data."
          }
        }
